Henrikh Mkhitaryan has fallen in love with life at AS Roma after tough spells at United and Arsenal. His first child was born in Rome + he has become a key player under Paolo Fonseca. Player hopes Roma can strike &pound;10m deal with Arsenal who are holding out for more. [<br />
@MailSport<br />
]

Lukas Podolski: &quot;I didn&rsquo;t get enough game time at Arsenal. I felt that I performed well and didn&rsquo;t get the minutes I deserved. On the other hand, if you look at my stats, I played in about 80 matches and was directly involved in lot of goals by scoring/assisting.&quot;<br />
<br />
Lukas Podolski on Serge Gnabry time at Arsenal: &quot;He was unlucky and had few injuries. He did well in training. Off the pitch we spent  lot of time together, going for dinner. But sometimes football is like that, or you find a manager who gives you more confidence.&quot;

